            "title": "黑期高水30點 重磅港股ADR變動不大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時07分升40點或0.16%，報25807點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報25806點，較香港上日現貨收市高32點或0.13%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣603.4元，較上日香港收市高1.42元或0.24%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣147元，較上日香港收市低0.19元或0.13%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣103.2元，較上日香港收市低0.04元或0.04%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣113.1元，較上日香港收市高0.28元或0.25%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣39.1元，較上日香港收市低0.11元或0.29%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣123.3元，較上日香港收市高1.01元或0.83%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣82.8元，較上日香港收市高0.16元或0.19%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣407.2元，較上日香港收市低0.4元或0.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣66.1元，較上日香港收市高0.12元或0.18%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.6元，較上日香港收市低0.02元或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報25818點，升30點，較上日恒指收市25774點，高水44點。科指期貨夜市收報5497點，較上日科指收市高水8點；國指期貨夜市收報8927點，較上日國指收市高水13點。</p>\n</div>",
